
                                ===== 
                                Bossa
                                -----
                        A java workflow engine.
                        =======================

Dependencies
============

Bossa requires the following software to run:

 * J2SE 1.2 JRE
   Notes: The newer the better, 1.4 works fine (and fast).
   URL: http://java.sun.com/

 + Prevayler >=2.00.001
   URL: http://www.prevayler.org/

 + BSF =cvs20030213
   Notes: We need a unreleased version of BSF, get it from our download page.
   URL: http://jakarta.apache.org/bsf/

 + Rhino >=1.5R2 <=1.5R3
   URL: http://www.mozilla.org/rhino/

For convenience, we provide an archive with the binaries marked with a +
in our download page.

Bossa requires the aditional software to compile:

 * J2SE 1.2 SDK
   Notes: The newer the better, 1.4 works fine (and fast).
   URL: http://java.sun.com/

 * Ant
   Notes: We use 1.5.1, older versions may work.
   URL: http://ant.apache.org/

 * JUnit >=3.8.1
   Notes: For the tests only.
   URL: http://www.junit.org/
